Title: GSE159526 raw data (rgset)
Description: The GSE159526 package contains data derived from Illumina HumanMethylationEPIC DNA methylation microarrays (Yuan et al. 2021), consisting of 19 term and 9 first trimester placental chorionic villi and matched cell-sorted samples, formatted raw unprocessed data as an RGChannelSet object for integration and normalization using most of the existing Bioconductor packages.

Title: GSE159526 processed data
Description: The GSE159526 package contains data derived from Illumina HumanMethylationEPIC DNA methylation microarrays (Yuan et al. 2021), consisting of 19 term and 9 first trimester placental chorionic villi and matched cell-sorted samples. This is data processed as described in Yuan 2021, formatted as a [[FILL THIS IN]] object for immediate analysis
